flowchart TD
  Start([Start]) --> Open[Overseas Import Site opens profile management]
  Open --> Select[Select site profile to update]
  Select --> UpdateBranch{Update Types}
  UpdateBranch -->|Profile| UpdateProfile[Update Site profile name/info]
  UpdateBranch -->|Delivery Times| UpdateTimes[Update delivery times ship/air]
  UpdateBranch -->|Catalog| UpdateCatalog[Update merchandise catalog]
  
  UpdateProfile --> Submit[Submit changes]
  UpdateTimes --> Submit
  UpdateCatalog --> Submit

  Submit --> Validate{Times are positive integers?}
  Validate -->|No| Error[Display Validation Error & Prompt re-entry]
  Error --> UpdateTimes
  Validate -->|Yes| Save[System saves changes & Notifies Ordering Department]
  Save --> End([End])
